data.title: So thankful for all the fans who came out to Forest Lawn last Friday to pay their respects at Sammy’s gravesite! It was a very successful...
data.meta_description:
901 likes, 33 comments - officialsammydavisjr on December 11, 2023: "So thankful for all the fans who came out to Forest Lawn last Friday to pay their respects at Sammy’s gravesite! It was a very successful event and we hope to see the attendance grow each year as we come closer to Sammy’s centennial in 2025.
